        <h3><strong>How Fan Game Cube Works</strong></h3>
        <p>
          Fan Game Cube transforms how fans interact with the sports they love by tokenizing playing fields across any sport—from chess boards to football pitches. This creates both a novel fan experience and a sustainable revenue channel for clubs.
        </p>
        <p>
          At its core, fans purchase NFTs representing virtual zones of real playing fields. These aren't static collectibles—they're dynamic assets tied directly to live in-game events like goals, plays, and key moments. As real-world action unfolds in their owned zones, fans earn points and rewards.
        </p>
        <p>
          The <a href="https://docs.bws.ninja/marketplace-solutions/bws.nft.gamecube" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">NFT Game Cube platform</a> handles all the technical complexity, allowing clubs to focus entirely on what matters most: engaging their fanbase. This turnkey approach makes it accessible to sports organizations of all sizes.
        </p>
        <p>
          The solution serves a broad market—sports clubs, leagues, athlete brands, and IP holders—all seeking to bridge the gap between traditional fandom and digital innovation. Most importantly, it's built for regular Web2 users who've never touched cryptocurrency before.
        </p>
        <figure style="float: right; margin: 0 0 1rem 1rem; min-width: 500px; max-width: 600px;">
